A simple and interactive web tool that captures your keyboard inputs and displays the character live on the screen with a clean, minimalist design.

# FEATURES:-
* Live input detection.
* Minimalist UI.
* Fast & lightweight.
* Learning Tool.

# Language is used:-
* HTML5:- Basic structure for the display area.
* CSS3:- For the grey background and centered, large font styling.
* JavaScript:- Uses keydown event listeners to capture and update the UI
